verbose_text: DAGLalpha overexpression did not affect the angle at which GCs approached COS-7-DAGLalpha cells (XREF_FIG), the length of cholinergic neurites (XREF_FIG), the distance between cholinergic and COS-7 somata (XREF_FIG), and the survival of p75 NTR+ neurons in vitro (data not shown), excluding delayed morphogenesis or neuronal migration as confounding factors.
